des:
Come home to comfort all year round with Glen Dimplex Connect. Glen Dimplex Connect helps you to connect your supported Dimplex and NOBO appliances through a virtual remote system, meaning you can control your appliances from anywhere! Arrive home and enjoy a heated and/or cooled home by remotely setting your chosen temperature through the remote system. 
Glen Dimplex Connect is the ONE convenient app you need to connect you to your supported Dimplex heaters and coolers and NOBO panels. With the app, you can remotely activate and manage supported products, schedule appliance functions and timers (if applicable) and best of all create the convenience of arriving home in comfort. 
This application only works on selected Dimplex and NOBO products. A stable internet connection is required.

You can simply ask Alexa to control your dehumidifier. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Glen Dimplex Connect” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “Glen Dimplex Connect” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Glen Dimplex Connect” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Glen Dimplex Connect” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Glen Dimplex Connect” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on dehumidifier”
“Alexa, turn off dehumidifier.”
“Alexa, set the Dehumidifier to 35% humidity.”
“Alexa, set the Dehumidifier speed to high.”
